narrative:
This was a focused inspection of the 7 elephants at the facility: Talia (female, 6-8 years old) , Xolani (female, 7-9
years old), Dakari  (female, 8-10 years), Titan (male, 7(cid:19)-9 years old), Simunye (female about 20 years old), Arusi
(female about 6 years old), and Stephanie (female, 44 years old).
No non-compliant items identified during this inspection. 
 
Inspection and exit interview conducted with facility representatives and Margaret A Shaver, VMO in attendance.
